These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-1::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, cauliflower, raspberry, strawberry
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, pop, salsa, country
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, guinea-pig, chinchilla, rat
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, van, jet-ski, skateboard
 1. the person driving the van is the fan of pop##1
 2. the person eating raspberry is the fan of salsa##1
 3. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the fan of punk##1
 5. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 7. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
 8. the fan of country is somewhere to the left of the fan of salsa##5
 9. the fan of country is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
10. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##5
11. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the right of the person eating strawberry##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |    4     |
| Food          | strawberry     | cauliflower   | orange | raspberry |
| Music-Genre   | pop | punk    | country   | salsa    |
| Pet           | chinchilla       | rat   | guinea-pig   | rabbit     |
| Transport     | van       | boat | skateboard  | jet-ski      |

