.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, fanta, 7up, juice
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, romance, superhero, action
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, lizard, guinea-pig, turtle
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, van, airplane, quad-bike
 1. the person watching superhero movies is on the far right##1
 2. the owner of the guinea-pig is in an odd position##4
 3. the owner of the turtle is the person drinking water##1
 4. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
 5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person watching fantasy movies is between the person watching action movies and the person drinking fanta##2
 8. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the person driving the van##5
 9. the owner of the lizard is the person watching action movies##1
10. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
11. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |      4       |
| Beverage      | fanta       | water | juice     | 7up     |
| Movie-Genre   | romance      | fantasy       | action | superhero |
| Pet           | guinea-pig       | turtle    | lizard     | rabbit         |
| Transport     | quad-bike | airplane     | helicopter     | van       |

