 3. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the fan of d&b##5
 4. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5
 5. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person eating orange##1
 6. the owner of the goat is between the fan of salsa and the fan of country##2
 7. the fan of trance is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the mouse##5
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is in an even position##4
10. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person eating orange##1
11. the person watching musical movies is the owner of the hedgehog##1
12. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the left of the person eating pineapple##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |   3    |    4    |
