.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, milk, mirinda, lemonade
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, onion, eggplant, tomato
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, dancer, mechanic, freelancer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, superhero, spy, thriller
 1. the freelancer is somewhere to the right of the person eating tomato##5
 2. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
 3. the bartender is between the person drinking 7up and the freelancer##2
 4. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the freelancer##5
 5. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3
 6. the person drinking lemonade is in an odd position##4
 7. the mechanic is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 8. the person eating grapefruit is somewhere to the right of the dancer##5
 9. the mechanic is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
10. the bartender is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
11. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
12. the person eating onion is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3      |        4        |
| Beverage      | lemonade   | 7up | milk   | mirinda          |
| Food          | onion    | tomato        | eggplant     | grapefruit          |
| Job           | dancer | mechanic        | bartender | freelancer |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller    | animation     | spy      | superhero        |

