.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, juice, cola, lemonade
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, nurse, librarian, firefighter
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, mystery, horror, western
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, boat, bus, jet-ski
 1. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
 3. the firefighter is on the left or right of the writer##3
 4. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 5. the nurse is between the librarian and the person watching western movies##2
 6. the person watching horror movies is in an odd position##4
 7. the librarian is the person watching mystery movies##1
 8. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
 9. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
10. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
11. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
12. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the writer##1
13. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person watching horror movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | cola   | lemonade      | juice | tea     |
| Job           | firefighter   | writer  | nurse        | librarian |
| Movie-Genre   | family     | western     | horror      | mystery   |
| Transport     | boat | bus | jet-ski          | tram     |

