.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-20::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, pomegranate, onion, cabbage
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, accountant, software-developer, chef
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, zombie, sports, crime
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, r&b, metal, jazz
 1. the person eating onion is somewhere to the right of the person watching zombie movies##5
 2. the fan of jazz is the person eating avocado##1
 3. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the fan of indie##5
 4. the librarian is in an even position##4
 5. the accountant is on the left of the fan of metal##1
 6. the fan of indie is somewhere to the right of the fan of r&b##5
 7. the software-developer is the person watching crime movies##1
 8. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the left of the librarian##5
 9. the fan of metal is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
10. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating onion##5
11. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating cabbage##5
12. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the left of the person eating onion##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | avocado | onion  | cabbage    | pomegranate       |
| Job           | accountant  | chef | software-developer | librarian  |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie    | sports   | crime  | animation     |
| Music-Genre   | jazz      | metal    | r&b        | indie |

 